  <hr /><a name="annulus"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">ANNULUS</dt>
  <dd>A term sometimes used in heraldic blazoning when the main charge (or charges) is (or are) surrounded by an annulet - see &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dva3.html#annulet">annulet</a>&rsquo; (also &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvb6.html#blazon">blazon</a>&rsquo;).
